@page "/careers"

<PageTitle>Work With Us</PageTitle>

<div class="container my-5 text-center">
    <!-- Section Headline -->
    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2" style="color: #f8b500;">Gotorz</h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <h4 class="fw-bold mb-4">Join Our Team</h4>

    <!-- White Content Box -->
    <div class="mx-auto p-4 text-start"
         style="
             background-color: white;
             border-radius: 5px;
             border: 1px solid lightgrey;
             box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
             max-width: 1000px;
             line-height: 1.8;
         ">

        <p><strong>Want to join the Gotorz team and help us organize travel experiences across the globe?</strong></p>

        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">Are You Looking for a Job?</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>✔️ Yes</li>
            <li>✔️ Tired of routine and want to be creative?</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
            We're looking for motivated young men and women interested in working in all areas of the tourism sector.
            Some applicants may not have prior experience in tourism or customer service — that’s okay!
            However, you must meet the following criteria:
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li>Fluency in Swedish, German, or another European language (spoken + written) in addition to Arabic.</li>
            <li>Strong communication skills and ability to use email and social media effectively.</li>
            <li>Good computer skills and a professional tone when communicating with clients.</li>
            <li>Ability to work under pressure, be organized, and maintain deadlines.</li>
            <li>
                Prior work or internship experience in:
                <ul>
                    <li>Customer service</li>
                    <li>Tourism/marketing</li>
                    <li>Sales or social media management</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>Passion for working in the tourism and travel industry.</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">What Does Gotorz Offer?</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>Good pay.</li>
            <li>Flexible work (freelance or contract-based depending on country laws).</li>
            <li>A fun, remote-friendly work environment with the possibility of meeting the Gotorz team in Europe.</li>
            <li>Free or discounted travel tickets and training courses in tourism.</li>
            <li>Career development and long-term opportunities with us.</li>
        </ul>

        <h5 class="fw-bold mt-4">Apply Now and Start Your Journey With Us</h5>
        <p>
            Send your resume to: <a href="mailto:careers@gotorz.ae">careers@gotorz.ae</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
